description:
Doomsday (2008)

A lethal virus spreads throughout the British isles,infecting 
millions and killing hundreds of thousands. To contain the 
threat, acting authorities brutally quarantine the country as 
it succumbs to fear and chaos. The quarantine is successful. 
Three decades later, the Reaper virus violently resurfaces in 
a major city. An elite group of specialists, including Eden 
Sinclair, is urgently dispatched into the still-quarantined 
country to retrieve a cure by any means necessary. Shut off 
from the rest of the world, the unit must battle through a 
andscape that has become a waking nightmare.
